      "text": "BUREAU FILE 62-83894, Serials 80, 184, and 225",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "During my absence, at 11:50 A.M. today, [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "in the office of Drew Pearson, called and talked with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "[REDACTED] wick. [REDACTED] stated Pearson has been in contact with",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Dr. [REDACTED] (Phoenix telephone number [REDACTED] concerning",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "photographs which the above captioned took of flying discs in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "the Phoenix area in July of 1947.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "[REDACTED] states that Dr. [REDACTED] told Pearson today",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "that the FBI borrowed his negatives of the flying discs and when",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "asked for their return the FBI told Rhodes the negatives were not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "available.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "[REDACTED] asked whether there is any truth to this",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "statement of [REDACTED] and what the FBI knew about him.",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "It appears that Pearson is interested in using the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "photographs on his television program and is desirous of borrowing",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "them from the Bureau or having them returned to Dr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "BACKGROUND:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Bureau files reflect that on August 29, 1947, a Mr.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "[REDACTED], called at the Phoenix Office exhibiting",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "credentials reflecting he represented A-2, Fourth Air Force,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Hamilton Field, California. He asked an Agent to accompany",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "him to interview [REDACTED] who previously reported the",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "photographing of a flying disc in Phoenix on the afternoon of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "July 7, 1947.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "The Phoenix Office contacted SAC Harry Kimball of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "San Francisco Office and Mr. [REDACTED] verified the fact that [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "came to Phoenix as a representative of Colonel [REDACTED] of",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "Hamilton Field, and it was suggested the Phoenix Office assist",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "[REDACTED] not in investigating [REDACTED], but in simply talking with",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "Dr. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
