      "text": "[REDACTED] had requested the negatives from [REDACTED] who did not have",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "them in his immediate possession. [REDACTED] stated, however, he",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
